query.name: taxi_trips_by_borough_and_year

data.generatedSql:
SELECT
  location.borough,
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM taxi_trips.Pickup_DateTime) AS year,
  COUNT(*) AS num_trips
FROM `governed-data-1pqzajgatl`.`taxi_dataset`.`taxi_trips` AS taxi_trips
INNER JOIN `governed-data-1pqzajgatl`.`taxi_dataset`.`location` AS location
  ON taxi_trips.PULocationID = location.location_id
GROUP BY 1, 2;
